Directory: data/src-easy

This is supposed to contain the basic types of files/directory that could be
synchronized:
- classic directories with subdirs
- hidden directories (starting by a point)
- regular files
- symbolic links
- elements with different access right (cf .hiddendirectory, .hiddendirectory/secret)

Note that none of the filenames contains strange characters 

Directory content: 

          ./.hiddendirectory
          ./.hiddendirectory/secret
          ./dir
          ./dir/script.sh
          ./dir/subdir
          ./dir/subdir/subfile.txt
          ./file.txt
          ./link.txt
          ./README



================================================================================
